entry.title: ISIS Was Staging Comeback When U.S. Raid Led to Leader's Death
entry.content: The terrorist organization has regrouped in the three years since it lost its territory in Iraq and Syria, but its comeback has suffered a blow with the killing of Abu Ibrahim al-Hashimi al-Qurayshi.
